snippet.textDisplay: In my childhood   me my friends used to sing that song in every summer  season. I can remind that we were singing that song with a frog in head .we were likely going every house and sing that song. and my friends  threw water  on us....And we were rolling on the muddy ground with singing that song  literally we were praying for rain. That was an amazing memory and i miss those days badly....
